<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Page Not Found - 404 Error</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #343a40;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>404 Error - Page Not Found</h1>
        <p>The page you are looking for might have been removed, had its name changed, or is temporarily unavailable.</p>
        <p>Please check the URL for spelling errors, then <a href="/">click here</a> to go to the homepage.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
